{"tid":475663,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"一拳收工 南非拳王11秒KO對手","createTime":"2017-11-21T10:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T17:08:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"44f3ab4315bfeaca40ae699f0a2ed6192706e96d","tid":475663,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:22:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171121/20221215\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171121%2F20221215&d=I3169T1L%2FPFmetaPytazgROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=502e41cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171121%2F20221215&h=d18776db\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171121/20221215</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一拳收工<br />\n南非拳王11秒KO對手<br />\n<br />\n7,641<br />\n<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n上周六晚在北愛爾蘭舉行的一場拳王衞冕戰，衞冕冠軍的拳手用11秒就技術性擊倒挑戰者，刷新世界冠軍戰史上最快擊倒對手紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n在貝爾法斯特SSE體育館舉行世界拳擊組織（WBO）雛量級拳賽，29歲南非衞冕冠軍泰特（Zolani Tete）第一回合一出拳，就擊倒同鄉對手戈尼亞（Siboniso Gonya），那時只是鐘聲響起後6秒。<br />\n<br />\n拳證發現倒地的戈尼亞不省人事，5秒後宣佈比賽終止，讓台邊醫生上台檢查他的傷勢。戈尼亞要戴氧氣罩協助呼吸，不久後蘇醒並能站起來。<br />\n<br />\n泰特的閃電攻勢，刷新WBO超雛量級前拳王希門尼斯（Daniel Jimenez）1994年17秒技術性擊倒對手的紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約郵報  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n靚媽唔識老　仲係少女樣同囡囡分唔倒<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n【今日笑一笑】零食不停送入口　喵星人襲地球得手？"},{"pid":"095141d6cc70b7c1de4def84d04dbf409d2d7471","tid":475663,"uid":7090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T17:08:21.000Z","msg":"想睇薯君如同佢打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}